casebody.data:
SAINT PETER'S HEALTHCARE SYSTEM, et al., petitioners,
v.
Laurence KAPLAN. No. 16-86. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 2, 2016.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted. The case is consolidated *547and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
